Details.description:
.gg/typesoul - Make sure to join for CODES!!

Controls:
Left Alt - Shift-lock
Ctrl + K - Monster transformations/Mask rip
J - Reaper weapon
Ctrl + J - Reaper transformation/Monster transformation
Q - Dash
Z X C - Reaper skills/Partial Moveset
T G - Reaper/Monster/Volt Moveset
R - Critical
N - Inventory/Skill tree
M - Meditate
P - Purify Lost Soul
B - Grip/Eat if Monster
V - Carry
Comma - Toggle map markers inside SS

Developers:
CosmicReflection, TheNotDave, Tamayaren, kingcowoe, NuovaPrime, eduardobrg, sylenox,  nosrepp, CanadianMRE, CristiGmer25 - Scripter
nosrepp, eduardobrg, Quroven, kingcowoe, sylenox - VFX
Khaotxc, sylenox - Animator
4Data, sylenox - Modeler
drakoooos, Tamayaren - UI Artist
cartier361 - Builder

Contributors: invictal (Scripting), yuxnMeki (UIs), TheGreatAnubis (Modeler), earlvr (Clothing),
StormVegitto (Clothing), Rakuraii (Clothing), haniyura(Scripting), K1LLUAA

Full credits in the main menu.
